{
  "id": "adv_main_01_11_03",
  "title": "星見編3章3話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（――翌日は東京でレッスンだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The next day‚ the girls have lessons in Tokyo.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、本戦は今までみたいにはいきませんわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The way we’ve performed thus far won’t be enough to win the main match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.221473979949951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "練習のスケジュール、組んでみました\nどうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made a rehearsal schedule.\nWhat do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.015328900019329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……夜の十時までー！？\n朝六時に練習を開始",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…and we don’t stop until 10:00 at night?!\nWe start practicing at 6:00 in the morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.248662233352661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "全然、休みがない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No breaks at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.74866223335267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "このくらいしないと、本戦では勝てないと\nすずちゃんが言っていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ unless we do this much‚ we won’t win the main match.\nThat’s what Suzu said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.02458058993022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.891247256596884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "大体、東京のスタジオで六時スタートなんて\n始発で来ても間に合わないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ 6:00 in the morning at the studio in Tokyo?\nEven if we take the first train‚ we won’t make it on time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.77099784215292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよー\nすずちゃん、バカ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right!\nSuzu‚ are you dumb?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.90433117548626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why me?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.23766450881959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、そろそろ、練習に戻りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ let’s get back to practice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.03766450881959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。ストレッチ、一緒にやろう\n琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good idea. Let’s stretch together‚\nKotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.92736961046855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "これ、誰の声？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whose voice is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.89403627713523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "さあ……でも、聞いたことあるような\n……もしかして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know… but I think I’ve heard it somewhere.\nCould it be…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.610181450843825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "――さくら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.314104421933514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 60.2807710868617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、昨日までと違うような気がするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it sounds different from before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9807710868617,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5808.072694142645,
          "startTime": 66.78884378100435
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7003.083976109813,
          "startTime": 67.98385506297151
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……私、行ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go check.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.65551044767102,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.95052172963818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 70.61718839630483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら\nどういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura.\nWhat do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5838550629715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.84911602164307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "今の……\n昨日までと、歌い方違ったみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your singing just now‚\nit sounded different from before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.88244935497642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが\nちょっと別の歌い方も試してみたいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura said\nshe wanted to try singing in a different style.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9824493549764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "別の声も出ないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She thought her voice could sound different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6864492176473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……どうして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.56386415943501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "特に理由は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No reason in particular.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.79719749276833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "本当に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.06576886956887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけ、外で話してもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we talk outside for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.63243553623549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 102.83243553623555
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 102.83243553623555
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 103.03243553623552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、あの後、麻奈さんについてもう一度調べたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did some research on Mana yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.86576886956875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんについて……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You researched my sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.69910220290224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 110.56576886956891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。どこで生まれて、どうやってアイドルになって\nどんなに人気があったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Where she was born‚ how she became an idol‚\nhow popular she was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.66576886956896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
